{"tid":960342,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"公開日本寵物用品網批發價","createTime":"2018-12-29T10:48:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-13T23:57:20.000Z","uid":188810,"like":13,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"f326977d64af7ff71af971863ecf3d951d9a6a1b","tid":960342,"uid":188810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T10:48:03.000Z","msg":"今年同個養開貓的朋友夾份開左間主要賣日本貓零食網店<br />\n<br />\n做左一排都冇咩生意, 索性公開個批發價<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.petpochitto.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.petpochitto.com&d=d%2B5og5DsWzy3G5ml3I43o49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=cabe2076\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.petpochitto.com</a><br />\n以上網站係批發網, 大家回覆條貨品link我就公開批發價~~貓狗魚倉鼠兔仔咩貨都得<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r6br34y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr6br34y.png&h=a59fc227&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t3Zk8we.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft3Zk8we.png&h=b3076067&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n先公開兩件貨<br />\n<br />\n同埋想問下其實大家覺得只賣呢d零食唔賣糧有冇得做? <br />\n仲諗緊新一年壇野仲堅唔堅持落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6967b1e9c104b6ebe46d622db3d1d6eb863947b6","tid":960342,"uid":40470,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T10:50:43.000Z","msg":"買過<br />\n<br />\n樓主食水好深<br />\n<br />\n奸商<br />\n<br />\n仲有d零食好近期"},{"pid":"ec233694d701574e65cf18141e7cb11428a76a2a","tid":960342,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T10:51:12.000Z","msg":"抵你死最好蝕多d死奸商"},{"pid":"a72ed07a52034bc53ea77e9fad6b33e5eb7c39b7","tid":960342,"uid":155431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T10:54:40.000Z","msg":"小白執士呢？"},{"pid":"89954c26b5b24f8a1a580ae258c754acaae46b8b","tid":960342,"uid":188810,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T10:59:48.000Z","msg":"鋪頭食水就深, 我每包都係賺$10, 仲未計運費, 又要交收, 都唔知做黎為